OL,3,CTeenager followed girl for 45 minutes
OL,4,Cbefore fatal stabbing, court told
OL,6,FA teenage killer followed his 15-year-
OL,7,Fold victim for 45 minutes around a
OL,8,Ftown centre before he stabbed her to
OL,9,Fdeath down an alleyway, a court heard.
OL,11,FHolly Newton was repeatedly stabbed by
OL,12,Fa 16-year-old boy, who cannot be
OL,13,Fidentified due to his age, in Hexham,
OL,14,FNorthumberland, on January 27 last
OL,15,Fyear.
