OL,3,CTeenager followed girl for 45 minutes
OL,4,Cbefore fatal stabbing, court told
OL,6,FThe youth, now 17, is on trial at
OL,7,FNewcastle Crown Court and has admitted
OL,8,Fmanslaughter but denies murdering her
OL,9,Fafter she finished school that
OL,10,Fafternoon and was walking around shops
OL,11,Fwith friends.
OL,13,FOpening the prosecution case on
OL,14,FThursday 18 July, David Brooke KC,
OL,15,Fsaid the defendant knew Holly, who
OL,16,Flived in Haltwhistle and went to
OL,17,Fschool in Hexham.
