OL,3,CTeenager followed girl for 45 minutes
OL,4,Cbefore fatal stabbing, court told
OL,6,FThe youth left school early and went
OL,7,Fto Hexham where he followed Holly and
OL,8,Fher friends "from a distance", the
OL,9,FCrown said.
OL,11,F"It is quite clear he was being
OL,12,Fcareful not to be seen by them for the
OL,13,Fnext 45 minutes or so," Mr Brooke said.
OL,15,FHolly and a different teenage boy went
OL,16,Fto a pizza shop at around 4.45pm that
OL,17,Fafternoon and the defendant waited at
OL,18,Fa bus stop outside, where he then
OL,19,Fasked to speak to her.
