OL,3,CTeenager followed girl for 45 minutes
OL,4,Cbefore fatal stabbing, court told
OL,6,FMr Brooke said Holly was "not at all
OL,7,Fhappy" to see the defendant but she
OL,8,Feventually agreed to speak to him down
OL,9,Fan alleyway.
OL,11,F"What Holly didn't know was that (the
OL,12,Fdefendant) had brought a knife with
OL,13,Fhim," Mr Brooke said.
OL,15,FIn less than a minute, the defendant
OL,16,Finflicted 36 knife wounds on Holly,
OL,17,Fstabbing her 12 times and slashing her
OL,18,F19 times.
OL,20,FShe suffered a further five defensive
OL,21,Finjuries to her hands.
