OL,3,CTeenager followed girl for 45 minutes
OL,4,Cbefore fatal stabbing, court told
OL,6,FThe other teenage boy, alerted by her
OL,7,Fscreams, ran down the alleyway and
OL,8,Fgrabbed the defendant and was himself
OL,9,Fstabbed, the court heard.
OL,11,FPassersby and people from the pizza
OL,12,Fshop also helped, jurors were told.
OL,14,FHolly was taken to the Royal Victoria
OL,15,FInfirmary in Newcastle but she could
OL,16,Fnot be saved.
OL,18,FThe boy was arrested and told police
OL,19,Fhe took a kitchen knife to Hexham that
OL,20,Fday with the intention of hurting
OL,21,Fhimself, not Holly.
