OL,6,FHe claimed she had been "horrible" to
OL,7,Fhim when they spoke to each other near
OL,8,Fthe pizza shop and that his mind went
OL,9,Fblank.
OL,11,FThe boy denies murdering Holly and
OL,12,Fwounding the other boy with intent,
OL,13,Fand an alternative to that count of
OL,14,Fwounding.
OL,16,FHe has admitted possessing a knife,
OL,17,Fjurors were told.
